PG-only code change verified via: `go build ./internal/mthub/...` (clean, no errors).
The fix is correct: pg_try_advisory_xact_lock inside a transaction ensures the lock auto-releases on COMMIT/ROLLBACK, compatible with pgxpool connection pooling.
Full integration testing requires Redis accessible on localhost:6379.

